description:
Elegant and Exceptional Earrings Online From Priyaasi to Slay any Day!

 
For quintessential jewelry, this Earrings guide will be to the Rescue!
There is a thing about earrings for sure, and that is why there is a strong pull toward traditional women’s earrings. Every woman looks their best when they get accessorized with earrings be they simple or heavy earrings. Matchless earrings are available online which makes it undoubtedly difficult to choose, worry not we have narrowed your problem with this guide.
Select Earrings based on Face type:
We can easily find the shape of our face by outlining our face in the mirror, or if you are aware of your face shape and size it may be a bit easier to choose. So, what now? 
Well, there are typically different types of faces such as round, oval, diamond, square or box type, and rectangle, and obviously, every shape is unique and beautiful in its own way, also remember that earrings or any other jewelry are made to fit you, and you are not made to fit into them.
Earrings for Round Shape Face:
Round-shaped faces are often covered by the cheeks hence go for longer earrings, dangler earrings, drop earrings, hoops, teardrop earrings, and ear spikes would enhance your facial look. 
Earrings for Oval Shape Face:
Oval shape face triangle-shaped studs, hoops, and almost every type of earrings can do their best to fit your face
Earrings for Square Shape Face: 
Square shape face seems to look more like a box hence to enhance the face angles try oversized hoops to come out of the face and hang freely
Earrings for Diamond Shape Face:
Diamond shape faces are almost equal to an inverted triangle shape where the forehead is broader than the cheek and chin, hence to be a showstopper go for studs, teardrop earrings, circular barbells, ear spikes, huggie earrings will complete the look
Earrings for Rectangle Shape Face:
Rectangular Shape face is as unique as the other shapes, hence choosing minimal to oversized chandelier earrings, cluster earrings will align with the beautiful and dominating wide forehead
Priyaasi Online Jewelry is one of the most popular jewelry brands and shopping sites for sophisticated, trendy, and contemporary designer jewelry. Show up your glamor by adoring the statement jewelry according to your face shape to effortlessly get ready for festivities, big days, weddings, parties, and other special events to let the heads turn your side and sing a chandbali-an song for you. You can find regular wear to party wear earrings online from Priyaasi Jewelry sets India. Find all these below-mentioned Indian earrings online on Distacart.
Hoop Earrings:

Hoops are classic picks, they add a chic look to your formal wear or work wear. Minimal yet the ultimate option for a damn rich aww-look. Hoop earrings are the best choice for girls too, buy earrings for girls online at Priyaasi jewelry as they have a wide range of online jewelry collections and uniquely designed accessories
Chandbali Earrings: 

Chandbali earrings are the cutest pair of earrings for any face shape, they give festive or bridal vibes, and are perfect to jazz up on special occasions, explore designer chandbali earrings from Priyaasi jewelry online 
Studs Earrings:

Studs are for every age group, simply never go out of class, when it comes to studs it is true to the line, a colorful gemstone, kundans or single white stone stud adds an extremely adorable and cleaner look and is suitable for daily wear, and office wear. Also, an oversized stud can be eye-catching statement earrings for your outfit
Dangler Earrings:

Dangler earrings are dainty enough to uplift the whole look and put together the beauty. It is a great choice to pick on any formal to casual wear
Jhumkas: 

Jhumkas are everyone’s favorite type of earrings, they look their best when adorned on a traditional outfit, Kurtis, or on Indo-Western attires. Popular Priyaasi Jhumkas online are sure to amaze your feminine look, go for gold-plated and beaded circular Jhumkas without any second thought
Cluster Earrings:

Cluster Earrings include dazzling layers and tiers, they are almost like extended danglers, they seem extremely stunning when come in gems and stones with an elaborated design, take a look at Priyaasi contemporary earrings online they offer adorable cluster earrings with different colors of stones and precious gems
Thread Earrings: 

Thread Earrings are lightweight, and elegant, available in different colors to compliment your outfits, usually they are made of silk threads with precious stones embedded in them. 
Teardrop Earrings: 

Buy contemporary teardrop earrings online from Priyaasi jewelry brand as they have rose gold plated stone studded handcrafted teardrop-shaped drop earrings in various models
Latest Design Priyaasi Earrings On Distacart:
